GogoSpeaks: Working to revive the conversational, storytelling aspect of fellowship and learning, gobela Nokulinda Mkhize established GogoSpeaks. Under the theme of purpose and prosperity, the fourth edition of this series looks to give patrons practical tools and guidance to maximise their potential while soothing their internal anxieties.
